message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

hello hehe nkaleave kz yung mga technicalz q kya e2 muna pangpromote n kaya ko (bka may maawa..)

join na kayo sa tfx events management! if mahilig kayo mag-cosplay, mag-stream ng fave games niyo, and marunong mag-shoutcast during games,,, kAMI NA ANG PERFECT PARA SAINYOOOO 🥰

and hindi lang pang-talents ang hanap sa department namin! nOPEEEEEE of course not! looking din kami ng mga memberz na marunong or skilled sa paghandle and pagmanage ng mga audiovisualz stuff during events! bagay din sa technicalz yung marunong mag-navigate ng OBS and discord server <333

to anyone interested,,, e2 na po yung link sa applicationz,,, need ko pa ba magbeg sainyo,,,,,

LINK: https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1H4tquRNgc/
LINK: https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1H4tquRNgc/
LINK: https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1H4tquRNgc/

PLSSSS MAGJOIN N KEUUUUU e2 na yon,,,, see u in tfx!

CC: Heather, Syd
